Alfred Workflow Nodejs Lib
=========

A small library providing helpers to create Alfred Workflow

## Installation

  npm install alfred-workflow-nodejs

## Usage
    # import AlfredNode instance
    ```
    var AlfredNode = require('alfred-workflow-nodejs');
    ```

    # get instance of workflow and Item class
    ```
    var workflow = AlfredNode.workflow;
    workflow.setName("example-alfred-workflow");
    var Item = AlfredNode.Item;
    
    # other helpers
    ```
    var storage = AlfredNode.storage;
    var utils = AlfredNode.utils;
    var settings = AlfredNode.settings;
    ```

## Tests

  npm test

## Documents
    # Workflow and Item: generating feedbacks
    - 

    - Example
    ```
    var workflow = AlfredNode.workflow;
    workflow.setName("example-alfred-workflow");
    var Item = AlfredNode.Item;
    
    var item1 = new Item({title: "item 1", subtile: "sub 1"});
    var item2 = new Item({title: "item 1", subtile: "sub 1", valid: true, icon: "icon.png", arg: "arg", uid: "uid", autocomplete: "autocomplete"});
    workflow.addItem(item1);
    workflow.addItem(item2);
    workflow.feedback();

    ```

